The Keiser Report  No. 114
= Max Keiser and Stacy Herbert =
Thursday, 20 January 2011


[sebaygo1]


Corrupt Kleptocracy!

Max and Stacy talk about fiscal pathology, Bill Daley 'getting it done' and oil prices role in the UK trade deficit. 

In the second half of the show, Max talks to David Malone, author of The Debt Generation.

 that counters the monotone of mainstream corporate media.
